        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Securing America's Critical Minerals Supply Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Energy to conduct ongoing assessments of and secure any energy resource that (1) is essential to the energy sector and energy systems of the United States, and (2) has a supply chain which is vulnerable to disruption.</p>]]>
        </text>
